{"tid":2037319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國歌法殺到】高中首日復課 多區學生校門外靜坐","createTime":"2020-05-27T02:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T10:00:04.000Z","uid":82450,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c06e646c362997ef4ab4cf10241652b4dfd8d681","tid":2037319,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4CO7A47UVIB6F35HTNTZ6CHH4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4CO7A47UVIB6F35HTNTZ6CHH4U.jpg&h=a45f5d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日是高中生復課日，但同時亦是立法會二讀《國歌法》之日。一班聖保羅書院高中生今早選擇在校門外靜坐，表達對法例損害香港言論自由的不滿。多名參與靜坐的學生均表示，政府如欲讓市民尊重國歌，應是尊重市民，令市民對國家心悅誠服，而非倒行逆施，強行以法例迫使市民服從。學生亦批評導致香港亂局的罪魁禍首，是過去一年持續漠視民意的特首林鄭月娥。學生靜坐期間，校方未有干擾。<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅書院今日復課，校方今早在校門安排教職員為返校高中學生量度體溫。在課堂開始前，約有30名學生在校門外靜坐，表達對《國歌法》即將二讀、以及北京人大繞過香港立法會直接頒布港版《國安法》的不滿。參與學生未有呼喊口號或展示標語、旗幟，校方亦末有干預。靜坐期間，曾有多輛警車在校門外駛過，車上警員雖有對學生指手劃腳，但未有下車截查或驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n參與靜坐的中五生Dexter，今天參與靜坐是為了聲援在外以不同方式抗衡《國歌法》通過的港人、抗議政權漠視民意，試圖強行通過《國歌法》、港版《國安法》，以及表達對特首林鄭月娥在過去數月抗疫不力的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n另一中五學生Owen續解釋，林鄭班子過去一年拒聽民意，終令香港的各方矛盾進一步激化，她應負上最大責任。他亦指，港府試圖以《國歌法》要求港人尊重國歌，北京政府亦試圖推行港版《國安法》撲滅香港異見聲音，但政府應思考市民反對的原因，虛心思考民憤源頭，「如果市民覺到你做得好，就自然會由心而發尊重國歌，根本唔使立法例。」他又稱，擔心港版《國安法》後，連平日在社交平台或校園與同學閒談政治議題時，均會遭到審查或舉報，令港人失去言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n同樣就讀中五的Marcus則表示，警方今日在多區重兵佈防，高姿態戒備，令不少人想起過去一年的警暴問題，他今天返校亦感壓力，擔心會因年輕而被截查。他又感謝學校在互相尊重的前提下，容許學生在課堂開始前表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200527/W5ZRRNVNAEEPB6S7FLNCCX7OF4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FW5ZRRNVNAEEPB6S7FLNCCX7OF4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=39851b24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FW5ZRRNVNAEEPB6S7FLNCCX7OF4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4cd6cdac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200527/W5ZRRNVNAEEPB6S7FLNCCX7OF4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"ecf40360ee38bcd3110802da4a8e6ec65fb795c3","tid":2037319,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e47d55b8e1f1c788923f0ba5f64c444723decf","tid":2037319,"uid":289106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻小朋友加油💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻"},{"pid":"9649bffad6637c6009644fe22c98217ce8f57361","tid":2037319,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f148d2ae2524e6649b7d69406201cd3d5a184f","tid":2037319,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c7f1eeb3f92c49ad32554baaa369058374586f","tid":2037319,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"手足好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1212428fc65ef82ef12065b2482c955b7dc85c","tid":2037319,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"